description: Charged with the task of getting the Gundam to Earth, the White Base and its crew of novices must try to outwit Zeon’s ace pilot. Meanwhile, Amuro Ray has discovered a second Gundam. Can he control this machine of unparalleled destructive power and help the colony’s survivors?

This volume continues after Ichigo's revelation about his sword and his powers, and the Wandenreich begin their second invasion of Seireitei.
